name: flake8-isort
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "flake8-isort" %}
{% set version = "4.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 26571500cd54976bbc0cf1006ffbcd1a68dd102f816b7a1051b219616ba9fee0

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - flake8 >=3.2.1,<6
    - isort >=4.3.5,<6

test:
  imports:
    - flake8_isort
  requires:
    - pip
  commands:
    - pip check

about:
  home: https://github.com/gforcada/flake8-isort
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: flake8 plugin that integrates isort .
  dev_url: https://github.com/gforcada/flake8-isort

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dopplershift
    - marcelotrevisani
    - xylar
